<item>
            <title>[LU-19510] lustre-initialization: ipv6 lnet_sock_create(): Error trying to bind</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19510</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/cb31f24f-4ec3-4036-a450-d6a31dab78fe&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/cb31f24f-4ec3-4036-a450-d6a31dab78fe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;lustre-initialization failed with the following error on the console:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt; Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: /usr/sbin/lnetctl lnet configure -a -l
 LNetError: 8459:0:(lib-socket.c:313:lnet_sock_create()) Error trying to bind to fd33:3981:3213:f010:0:5254:8e:564e/7988: rc = -99
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;and the autotest log shows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;/usr/sbin/lnetctl lnet configure -a -l
---
configure:
-     lnet: 
      errno: -100
      descr: ! &quot;LNet configure error: Network is down&quot;
...
Exit code: 156
&quot;auster exited unexpectedly&quot;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/117704&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/117704&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-553.76.1.el8_10.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/117704&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/117704&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-553.76.1.el8_lustre.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;Please provide additional information about the failure here&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;







&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
lustre-initialization lustre-initialization - &quot;auster exited unexpectedly&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
