                            <comment id="476052" author="cbordage" created="Fri, 24 Oct 2025 12:28:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It failed 40 times in one week.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="475775" author="adilger" created="Wed, 22 Oct 2025 20:37:53 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_logs/3f654bab-1f37-4632-8712-b2af8b904cd0/show_text&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_logs/3f654bab-1f37-4632-8712-b2af8b904cd0/show_text&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;IPv6: eth0: IPv6 duplicate address fd33:3981:3213:f010:0:5254:8e:564e used by 52:54:00:83:41:fd detected!
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;some problem with the network configuration where same address is getting assigned to multiple hosts?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=colmstea&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;colmstea&quot;&gt;colmstea&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jgwoun&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jgwoun&quot;&gt;jgwoun&lt;/a&gt;, please take a look.  Is that caused by images being installed with indentical IPv6 addresses or some breakage in DHCPv6 or???&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="475774" author="hornc" created="Wed, 22 Oct 2025 20:12:09 +0000"  >

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_logs/3f654bab-1f37-4632-8712-b2af8b904cd0/show_text&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_logs/3f654bab-1f37-4632-8712-b2af8b904cd0/show_text&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
